liber.edit.client
Class WysiwymMenuItem

java.lang.Object
  UIObject
      liber.edit.client.WysiwymMenuItem

public class WysiwymMenuItem
extends UIObject

A widget that can be placed in a com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.WysiwymMenuBar. Menu items can either fire a com.google.gwt.user.client.Command when they are clicked, or open a cascading sub-menu.
